{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"36228cafa3","title":"读斯大林《苏联社会主义经济问题》的批注","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0143b3e918","index":0,"year":1958,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"36228cafa3"}],"tags":[{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji41","name":"毛泽东全集第41卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/41-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji41":{"comments":[{"id":"0e833b9b71","publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东1958年三次读斯大林《苏联社会主义经济问题》时的批注。"}],"contents":[{"id":"66bee04bb4","type":"title","text":"读斯大林《苏联社会主义经济问题》的批注”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"0e833b9b71","type":"subtitle","text":"对于与一九五一年十一月讨论会","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"49253772ac","type":"paragraph","text":"有关的经济问题的意见","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"df54967e19","type":"paragraph","text":"一关于社会主义制度下经济法则的","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"b493cf64f2","type":"paragraph","text":"这是完全的","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"8955a32c31","type":"paragraph","text":"性质问题重要的一章。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"540e7e1c02","type":"subtitle","text":"…··第1页]","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"92505c34da","type":"paragraph","text":"政治经济学的特点之一就在于：它的法则与","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"f8cf5d7bd0","type":"paragraph","text":"自然科学的法则不同，不是长久不变的；政治经","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"98a9a21d41","type":"paragraph","text":"济学法则，至少是其中大多数，是在一定的历史","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"59a20210e6","type":"paragraph","text":"时期中发生作用的，在此以后，它们就让位给新","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"db7c5e6421","type":"paragraph","text":"的法则。但是原来的这些法则，并不是被消灭，","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"bd4b62fb1e","type":"paragraph","text":"而是由于出现了新的经济条件而失去效力，退出","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"8cbfafa386","type":"paragraph","text":"舞台，让位给新的法则，这些新的法则并不是由","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"15303b9dd2","type":"paragraph","text":"人们的意志创造出来，而是在新的经济条件的基","index":14,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"a212dba3c4","type":"paragraph","text":"础上产生的。","index":15,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"419f4a1565","type":"paragraph","text":"有人引证恩格斯的《反杜林论》，引证他如自由与必然下的这个公式：随着资本主义的消灭和生产资料","index":16,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"f30645f1a3","type":"paragraph","text":"的公有化，人们将获得支配自己生产资料的权","index":17,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"ad23f2bad1","type":"paragraph","text":"力，将获得解脱社会经济关系压道的自由，而成","index":18,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"2ca6b50a1c","type":"paragraph","text":"为自已社会生活的“主人”。恩格斯把这种自由","index":19,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"26439725f5","type":"paragraph","text":"叫作“被认识了的必然性”。完竞“被认识了的","index":20,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"e38a695155","type":"paragraph","text":"必然性”是什么意思呢？这就是说，人们认识了","index":21,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"411e1605c1","type":"paragraph","text":"客观的法则（“必然性”）之后，就会完全自觉","index":22,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"804fe28858","type":"paragraph","text":"地运用这些法则来为社会谋福利。正因为如此，","index":23,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"7603d6a75b","type":"paragraph","text":"所以恩格斯在同一地方说：","index":24,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"0575be1273","type":"paragraph","text":"“人们自己的社会行动的法则，直到现在都","index":25,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"c69fe96d58","type":"paragraph","text":"如同异已的、统治着人们的自然法则一样而与人","index":26,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"f3b11d39ac","type":"paragraph","text":"们相对立。这些法则将被人们熟练地运用起来，","index":27,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"d76a052796","type":"subtitle","text":"因而将服从他们的统治。”","index":28,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"7520dd5efd","type":"paragraph","text":"可见，恩格斯的这个公式，决不是对于那些","index":29,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"b47d87aa94","type":"paragraph","text":"以为在社会主义制度下可以消灭现存经济法则和","index":30,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"86044fb4c2","type":"paragraph","text":"创造新经济法则的人们有利的。恰恰相反，这个","index":31,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"9513f7c3f4","type":"paragraph","text":"公式不是要消灭经济法则，而是要认识它们和善","index":32,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"b5424a1e87","type":"paragraph","text":"于运用它们。[第4页]","index":33,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"86dbf42723","type":"paragraph","text":"苏维埃政权的特殊作用，是由下列两种情况","index":34,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"2863fcd311","type":"paragraph","text":"来决定的：第一，苏维埃政权不是以另一种测削","index":35,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"9c50df2cb2","type":"paragraph","text":"形式去代替一种剥削形式，如像以往革命中的情","index":36,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"063cd8d9f5","type":"paragraph","text":"形那样，而是消灭了任何剥削；第二，由于国内","index":37,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"865a92fe4b","type":"paragraph","text":"缺乏任何现成的社会主义经济的萌芽，苏维埃政","index":38,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"eee7cf6030","type":"paragraph","text":"权当时必得在所谓“空地上”创造新的经济","index":39,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"8f8b2a8887","type":"paragraph","text":"形式。","index":40,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"d29377569a","type":"paragraph","text":"我们有先例","index":41,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"41cc43875d","type":"paragraph","text":"这个任务无疑是困难而复杂的，是没有先例","index":42,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"421aef0c95","type":"paragraph","text":"在往后亿方的。然而，苏维埃政权光荣地完成了这个任务。年中，生产力性但是，它之所以完成了这个任务，并不是因为它质不会不发生变似乎消灭了现存的经济法则，“制定”了新的经化的，为了一定济法则，而仅仅是因为它依靠了生产关系一定要要适合它，生产适合生产力性质这个经济法则。当时我国的生产关系也得改变，力，特别在工业中的生产力，是具有社会性的，而且将有无数的但所有制的形式却是私人的，资本主义的。苏维","index":43,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"219ba29596","type":"subtitle","text":"改变","index":44,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"c78be84fa2","type":"paragraph","text":"埃政权依据生产关系一定要适合生产力性质这个","index":45,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"2cf765d35c","type":"paragraph","text":"经济法则，把生产资料公有化了，使之成为全体","index":46,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"12abff1d07","type":"paragraph","text":"人民的财产，因而消灭了剥削制度，创造了社会","index":47,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"54dfe5c3f1","type":"paragraph","text":"主义的经济形式。如果没有这个法则，不依靠这","index":48,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"5130e8e74c","type":"paragraph","text":"个法则，苏维埃政权是不能完成自己的任务的。","index":49,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"8e1e81dab8","type":"paragraph","text":"[第5~6页]","index":50,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"354f55979d","type":"paragraph","text":"有人说，我国国民经济有计划的（按比例","index":51,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"abf9b53bfe","type":"paragraph","text":"这是一个客的）发展的必然性，使苏维埃政权有可能来消灭观法则","index":52,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"1d59b32076","type":"paragraph","text":"现存的经济法则和创造新的经济法则。这是完全","index":53,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"364ecaa068","type":"paragraph","text":"不对的，不能把我们的各个年度计划和五年计划","index":54,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"1c7a4f3810","type":"paragraph","text":"跟国民经济有计划、按比例的客观经济法则混为","index":55,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"c884387167","type":"paragraph","text":"一谈。国民经济有计划发展的法则，是作为资本","index":56,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"33a872b5ca","type":"paragraph","text":"主义制度下竞争和生产无政府状态的法则的对立","index":57,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"b6c1b1a793","type":"paragraph","text":"物而产生的。它是当竞争和生产无政府状态的法","index":58,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"51a3e72931","type":"paragraph","text":"则失去效力以后，在生产资料公有化的基础上产","index":59,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"7f290da005","type":"paragraph","text":"我们是否研生的。它之所以发生了作用，是因为只有在国民究了、掌握了、经济有计划发展的经济法则的基础上，社会主义学会熟练地应用的国民经济才能进行。这就是说，国民经济有计了这个客观法划发展的法则，使我们的计划机关有可能去正确则？我们的计划地计划社会生产。但是，不能把可能同现实混为是否完全反映了一谈。这是两种不同的东西。要把这种可能变为","index":60,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"55af00b4ca","type":"paragraph","text":"现实，就必须研究这个经济法则，必须掌握它，这个客观法则？","index":61,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"5ed62bf27a","type":"subtitle","text":"注意","index":62,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"502f88cfd9","type":"paragraph","text":"必须学会熟练地应用它，必须制定出能完全反映","index":63,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"4acf00733d","type":"paragraph","text":"这个法则的要求的计划。不能说，我们的各个年","index":64,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"5f754c4ab9","type":"paragraph","text":"度计划和五年计划都完全反映出这个经济法则的","index":65,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"806a410dbf","type":"paragraph","text":"要求。[第6～7页]","index":66,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"99f9f67b56","type":"paragraph","text":"二关于社会主义制度下的商品生产问题","index":67,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"e3f70bd26c","type":"paragraph","text":"不明确","index":68,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"534aed6eb9","type":"paragraph","text":"某些同志断定说，党在我国取得了政权并把","index":69,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"a0671422b4","type":"paragraph","text":"生产资料收归国有以后，还保存商品生产，是作","index":70,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"6f3d0838da","type":"paragraph","text":"我们也有得不对的。他们认为，党在当时便应当消除商品","index":71,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"6305061f7c","type":"paragraph","text":"生产。关于这点，他们引了恩格斯如下的话来作【这】样的人","index":72,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"39d5249e96","type":"paragraph","text":"证明：","index":73,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"7ca9736dd1","type":"paragraph","text":"“一旦社会占有了生产资料，那末商品生产","index":74,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"bda79f7075","type":"paragraph","text":"将被消除，而产品对生产者的统治也随之消","index":75,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"8d8d978ef9","type":"paragraph","text":"除。”（见《反杜林论》）","index":76,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"1a1f4334f8","type":"paragraph","text":"这些同志是大错特错了。","index":77,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"955a3d3a7d","type":"paragraph","text":"我们现在还","index":78,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"4ad35fdb2a","type":"paragraph","text":"我们来分析一下恩格斯的这个公式吧。恩格只有一部分生斯的这个公式不能认为是十分明确的，因为其中产资料归全民没有指出，完竟是社会占有一切生产资料，还是所有。","index":79,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"b3b1655e9e","type":"paragraph","text":"只占有一部分生产资料，即一切生产资料转归全","index":80,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"3693cecb98","type":"paragraph","text":"民所有，还是仅仅一部分生产资料转归全民所","index":81,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"f098de9623","type":"paragraph","text":"有。这就是说，恩格斯的这个公式可以理解成这","index":82,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"775a4cf17f","type":"paragraph","text":"样，也可以理解成那样。","index":83,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"7490d8b3f1","type":"paragraph","text":"在《反杜林论》的另一个地方，恩格斯讲到","index":84,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"0b1491ef8f","type":"paragraph","text":"占有“一切生产资料”，讲到占有“生产资料的","index":85,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"8c486f6e32","type":"paragraph","text":"全部总和”。这就是说，恩格斯在他自己的公式","index":86,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"49eca16e59","type":"paragraph","text":"中所指的，不是把一部分生产资料收归国有，而","index":87,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"20680a107a","type":"paragraph","text":"是把一切生产资料收归国有，即不仅把工业中的","index":88,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"2f71886d3a","type":"paragraph","text":"生产资料，而且也把农业中的生产资料都转归全","index":89,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"df8628c344","type":"paragraph","text":"民所有。","index":90,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"9f4020a201","type":"paragraph","text":"一切归全","index":91,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"2e386b1c31","type":"paragraph","text":"由此可见，恩格斯所指出是这样的一些国民，才能废商业家，在那里，不仅在工业中，而且也在农业中，","index":92,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"9e8799cfef","type":"paragraph","text":"因而产品充资本主义和生产集中都充分发达，以致可以刹夺分发达","index":93,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"e23d9aef33","type":"paragraph","text":"全国的一切生产资料，并把它们转归全民所有。","index":94,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"9d01ac50d9","type":"paragraph","text":"因而，恩格斯认为，在这样的国家中，在把一切","index":95,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"c951154c7e","type":"paragraph","text":"生产资料公有化的同时，还应该消除商品生产。","index":96,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"f3b5f1714f","type":"paragraph","text":"这当然是正确的。","index":97,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"4e73b8ae6b","type":"paragraph","text":"在十九世纪末叶《反杜林论》出版的时候，","index":98,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"f209e33525","type":"paragraph","text":"直到现在，只有英国一国。","index":99,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"1e4851f217","type":"paragraph","text":"只有英国一个国家是这样的国家，在那里，工业","index":100,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"19d182de3c","type":"paragraph","text":"英国是否能和农业中的资本主义发展和生产集中已达到这样废商业，还是的高度，以致有可能在无产阶级取得政权时，把一个待研究的国内的一切生产资料转归全民所有，并且消除商问题。","index":101,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"f1e1470078","type":"paragraph","text":"品生产。","index":102,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"d69686fbe2","type":"paragraph","text":"看来还得生","index":103,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"9adf6ca1ac","type":"paragraph","text":"在这里，我搬开了在英国国民经济中占有巨产商品","index":104,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"30ce1a4a43","type":"paragraph","text":"大比重的对外贸易对于英国的意义这个问题。我","index":105,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"c5d1c7cde5","type":"paragraph","text":"以为只有研究了这个问题之后，才能最后解决在","index":106,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"451d506621","type":"paragraph","text":"英国无产阶级取得政权并把一切生产资料收归国","index":107,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"3b8523f353","type":"paragraph","text":"有以后商品生产的命运问题。","index":108,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"1388fee9c7","type":"paragraph","text":"美、法、","index":109,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"00bea554ec","type":"paragraph","text":"基至，不仅在十九世纪末叶，而且在现时也德、瑞、挪、还没有一个国家在农业中的资本主义发展和生产丹、荷、比、卢集中是已经达到了像我们在英国所看到的那种都不如英吗？","index":110,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"ed15094bc8","type":"paragraph","text":"程度。至于说到其余的国家，虽然那里的农村","index":111,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"ad41948247","type":"paragraph","text":"中有资本主义的发展，可是农村中却还有人数","index":112,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"39ee7dc394","type":"paragraph","text":"相当众多的中小私有生产者阶级，这些人的命","index":113,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"9bc3b3c489","type":"paragraph","text":"运是在无产阶级取得政权时应该予以确定的。","index":114,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"535a92fbba","type":"paragraph","text":"[第8～10页]","index":115,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"334abbf01b","type":"paragraph","text":".……","index":116,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"f5e9b071f2","type":"paragraph","text":"如果可以公有化的不是一切生产资料，而仅","index":117,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"0b4238c413","type":"paragraph","text":"仅是一部分生产资料，而无产阶级夺取政权的有","index":118,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"c5e52c62a4","type":"paragraph","text":"利条件又已经具备，那将怎么办呢，——无产阶","index":119,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"f0b7338a4b","type":"paragraph","text":"级是否应该茶取政权，在夺取政权以后是否必须","index":120,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"7ae307978e","type":"paragraph","text":"立即消灭商品生产呢？","index":121,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"0e88aac764","type":"paragraph","text":"对于这个问题，列宁在关子“粮食税”的几","index":122,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"792b8f5bf8","type":"paragraph","text":"篇著作以及有名的“合作运动计划”中，给了","index":123,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"dcd680cdd9","type":"paragraph","text":"回答。","index":124,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"e96d6b9837","type":"paragraph","text":"列宁的五","index":125,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"fb86eafcf2","type":"paragraph","text":"列宁的回答可以简括如下：条，我们都做","index":126,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"20aaffb123","type":"paragraph","text":"（甲）不要放过夺取政权的有利条件，无产了，并且建立了阶级应该夺取政权，不要等待到资本主义使千百人民公社，以全万中小个体生产者居民破产的时候；","index":127,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"276389c272","type":"paragraph","text":"（乙）剥夺工业中的生产资料，并把它们转力发展工业、农业和商业，列宁归全民所有：","index":128,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"7eeb3351d4","type":"paragraph","text":"（丙）至于中小个体生产者，那就要逐渐地是要以全力发展商业，问题还是把他们联合到生产合作社中，即联合到大规模的一个农民问题，农业企业、集体农庄中；","index":129,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"5de33f96e4","type":"paragraph","text":"（丁）以一切方法发展工业，为集体农庄建必须谨【慎小心。","index":130,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"7d8e49aa78","type":"paragraph","text":"立大规模生产的现代技术基础，并且不要剥夺集","index":131,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"387c24bfe1","type":"paragraph","text":"体农庄，相反地，要加紧供给它们头等拖拉机和","index":132,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"9469d6a0f5","type":"paragraph","text":"其他机器；","index":133,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"1b4c917130","type":"paragraph","text":"（戌）为了城市和乡村、工业和农业的经济","index":134,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"c61d9ae670","type":"paragraph","text":"结合，要在一定时期内保持商品生产（通过买","index":135,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"d84d12ebb9","type":"paragraph","text":"卖的交换）这个为农民唯一可以接受的与城市","index":136,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"deefb40e9b","type":"paragraph","text":"进行经济联系的形式，并且要以全力开展苏维","index":137,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"0827a97a35","type":"paragraph","text":"埃贸易，即国营贸易和合作社一集体农庄贸","index":138,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"be2ff704fc","type":"paragraph","text":"易，把所有一切资本家从商品流通中排挤出","index":139,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"ca572d1219","type":"paragraph","text":"去。「第11～12页]","index":140,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"1aad0886a4","type":"paragraph","text":"不要怕资本","index":141,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"d7991098aa","type":"paragraph","text":"有人说，商品生产在任何条件下总还是要引主义，因为不会导到而且一定会引导到资本主义。这是不对的。再有资本主义。","index":142,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"a3f907905f","type":"paragraph","text":"并非在任何时候，也不是在任何条件下都是如","index":143,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"916ebd0997","type":"paragraph","text":"此！不能把商品生产和资本主义生产混为一谈。","index":144,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"fd4d97a5d6","type":"paragraph","text":"这是两种不同的东西。资本主义生产是商品生产","index":145,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"f372e5ae2d","type":"paragraph","text":"的最高形式。只有存在着生产资料的私有制，只","index":146,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"b756d22bb1","type":"paragraph","text":"有劳动力作为商品出现在市场上，资本家能够购","index":147,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"69c4131c89","type":"paragraph","text":"买它并在生产过程中剥削它，因而只有在国内存","index":148,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"7ecfa2e526","type":"paragraph","text":"在着资本家剥削届佣工人的制度时，商品生产才","index":149,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"fe44cd8fee","type":"paragraph","text":"会引导到资本主义。资本主义生产是在这样的场","index":150,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"28ef761caa","type":"paragraph","text":"合开始的，即生产资料是集中在私人手里，而被","index":151,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"a78f915e1e","type":"paragraph","text":"副券了生产资料的工人不得不把自己的劳动力作","index":152,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"4a64adcbb3","type":"paragraph","text":"为商品出卖。没有这种情形，就没有资本主义","index":153,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"cf74e10b25","type":"paragraph","text":"生产。","index":154,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"794b5f5537","type":"paragraph","text":"但是，如果这些使商品生产转化为资本主义","index":155,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"2329d9f58c","type":"paragraph","text":"生产的条件已不存在，如果生产资料已经不是私","index":156,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"b9d6b2e185","type":"paragraph","text":"有财产而是社会主义财产，如果属佣劳动制度","index":157,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"51039629ac","type":"paragraph","text":"已经不存在，而劳动力已经不是商品，如果剂","index":158,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"30d3c9bdc2","type":"paragraph","text":"削制度早已消灭，那又怎么样呢？可不可以认","index":159,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"da4afe0f96","type":"paragraph","text":"为商品生产总还会引导到资本主义呢？不，不","index":160,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"646b76b0ee","type":"paragraph","text":"可以这样认为。要知道，我国社会正是生产资","index":161,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"6da7679766","type":"paragraph","text":"料私有制度、星佣劳动制度、测削制度早已不存","index":162,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"5e2642e176","type":"paragraph","text":"在了的社会。","index":163,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"779419ee5f","type":"paragraph","text":"决不能把商品生产看作是某种不依赖周围经","index":164,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"05d168aae6","type":"paragraph","text":"商品生产是","index":165,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"fdd2f80da9","type":"paragraph","text":"济条件而独立存在的东西。商品生产比资本主义否有用的工具。","index":166,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"77271e23c9","type":"paragraph","text":"生产更老些。它在奴隶制度下就存在过，并且替","index":167,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"35602e4503","type":"paragraph","text":"奴隶制度服务过，然而并没有引导到资本主义。","index":168,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"c09e095ca4","type":"paragraph","text":"它在封建制度下就存在过，并且替封建制度服务","index":169,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"976d649836","type":"paragraph","text":"过，可是，虽然它为资本主义生产准备了若干条","index":170,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"81bb971696","type":"paragraph","text":"件却没有引导到资本主义。如果注意到，在我","index":171,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"f2539aa15f","type":"paragraph","text":"国，商品生产没有像在资本主义条件下那样漫无","index":172,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"ec9de677a8","type":"paragraph","text":"限制和包罗一切地扩展着，它由于生产资料公有","index":173,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"6b34472745","type":"paragraph","text":"制的建立、星佣劳动制度的消灭和剥削制度的消","index":174,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"1f9ae09eaa","type":"paragraph","text":"灭等决定性的经济条件，而受到极严格的限制，","index":175,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"68b56cb5e0","type":"paragraph","text":"试问，为什么商品生产就不能在一定时期内同样","index":176,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"0e95c66f32","type":"paragraph","text":"地为我国社会主义社会服务而并不引导到资本主","index":177,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"a994b1d937","type":"paragraph","text":"义呢？","index":178,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"1878cf3193","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）劳动；","index":179,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"be238584c2","type":"paragraph","text":"有人说，在我国生产资料公有制已经建立，（二）土地；（三）而屋佣劳动制度和剥削制度已被消灭以后，商品工具：都是公社所生产的存在就失去了意义，因此就应该消除商品有的，因此产品也生产。是公社所有的。","index":180,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"a44bd0c71d","type":"paragraph","text":"这也是不对的。现今在我国，存在着社会主","index":181,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"290d59480d","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五二年义生产的两种基本形式：一种是国家的全民的形","index":182,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"1df4e8b8b8","type":"paragraph","text":"式，一种是不能叫做全民的集体农庄的形式。在国","index":183,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"8e75899f89","type":"paragraph","text":"家企业中，生产资料和产品是全民的财产。在集体","index":184,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"5e9b8d2524","type":"paragraph","text":"农庄的企业中，虽然生产资料（土地、机器）也属","index":185,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"f96e7297a1","type":"paragraph","text":"于国家，可是产品却是各个集体农庄的财产；因为","index":186,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"125b652ecb","type":"paragraph","text":"集体农庄中的劳动也如种籽一样，是它们自己所有","index":187,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"2b21a13a03","type":"paragraph","text":"的，而国家交给集体农庄永久使用的土地，事实上","index":188,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"d30994593f","type":"paragraph","text":"是由集体农庄当作自己的财产来支配的，不过它们","index":189,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"c6223c9907","type":"paragraph","text":"不能出卖、购买、出租或抵押这些土地。","index":190,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"115454b3bb","type":"paragraph","text":"这种情况就使得国家所能支配的只是国家企","index":191,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"c4b1cdd7a4","type":"paragraph","text":"业的产品，至于集体农庄的产品，只有集体农庄","index":192,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"2a489b1782","type":"paragraph","text":"才能作为自己的财产来支配。然而，集体农庄只","index":193,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"b01242d67e","type":"paragraph","text":"愿把自己的产品当作商品让出去，愿意以这种商","index":194,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"bd0d248bd2","type":"paragraph","text":"品换得它们所需要的商品。现时，除了经过商品","index":195,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"3720d88fe6","type":"paragraph","text":"的联系，除了通过买卖的交换以外，与城市的其","index":196,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"a9eafa8a1a","type":"paragraph","text":"三十年后他经济联系，都是集体农庄所不接受的。因此，还如列宁在时商品生产和商品流通，目前在我国，也像大约三那样。","index":197,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"3f5ab89e64","type":"paragraph","text":"十年以前当列宁宣布必须以全力扩展商品流通时","index":198,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"f1f634df8a","type":"paragraph","text":"什么时候，一样，仍是必要的东西。商品才可以消","index":199,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"d156afc552","type":"paragraph","text":"当然，在出现了有权支配全国一切消费品的失呢？","index":200,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"2ac1912baa","type":"paragraph","text":"一个无所不包的生产部门，来代替两种基本生产","index":201,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"cd36df8259","type":"paragraph","text":"部门即国营部门和集体农庄部门之后，商品流通","index":202,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"15f4343e57","type":"paragraph","text":"及其“货币经济”就会作为国民经济的不必要的","index":203,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"2bedeffe62","type":"paragraph","text":"因素而消失了。但是，只要这个条件还不具备，","index":204,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"a6e544bcc8","type":"paragraph","text":"只要还存在着两种基本生产部门的时候，商品生","index":205,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"3d9edd5a6e","type":"paragraph","text":"产和商品流通便应当作为我国国民经济体系中心","index":206,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"2e7853602b","type":"paragraph","text":"要的和极其有用的因素而仍然保存着。怎样来建","index":207,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"2e45fd4b9e","type":"paragraph","text":"立这种单一的统一的部门呢？是让国营部门干脆","index":208,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"fd444b5301","type":"paragraph","text":"香没集体农庄部门，——而这是很难设想的（因","index":209,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"e8915bf34c","type":"paragraph","text":"为这会被理解为对集体农庄的剥夺），——还是","index":210,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"49d2a7620e","type":"paragraph","text":"组织统一的全民的（有国家工业和集体农庄代表","index":211,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"df958c8eb6","type":"paragraph","text":"参加的）经济机构，即起初有权统计全国一切消","index":212,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"eb8abdf41b","type":"paragraph","text":"费品，而经过一个时期也有权，例如以产品交换","index":213,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"6c8a69f120","type":"paragraph","text":"方式来分配产品的经济机构呢？这是一个特别","index":214,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"1bb5b6b64e","type":"paragraph","text":"的、需要单独讨论的问题。","index":215,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"4fdefe4100","type":"paragraph","text":"不是普通的","index":216,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"4724efa27d","type":"paragraph","text":"可见，我国的商品生产并不是通常的商品生商品，而是特别产，而是特种的商品生产，是没有资本家参加的","index":217,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"c681666fb5","type":"subtitle","text":"商品。","index":218,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"435f221c08","type":"paragraph","text":"商品生产，这种商品生产基本上是与联合的社会","index":219,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"b8fde372ef","type":"paragraph","text":"限于个人消主义生产者（国家、集体农庄、合作社）的商品费品吗？不，在有关的。它的活动范围只限于个人消费品。显我国，农业和手然，它决不能发展为资本主义生产，而且它注定工业生产工具也了要和它的“货币经济”一起共同为发展和巩固是商品。是否会社会主义生产的事业服务。[第12～15页]导致资本主义呢？不。","index":220,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"ee2371f682","type":"paragraph","text":"两种劳动都","index":221,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"0e0cbb5d51","type":"paragraph","text":".....现在，在我国的制度下，说劳动力是商","index":222,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"81279595af","type":"paragraph","text":"品，说工人“被星佣”，这真是十分荒谓的，好是必要的。","index":223,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"b3ceaf1648","type":"paragraph","text":"像占有生产资料的工人阶级自己被自己届佣，把","index":224,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"665afac911","type":"paragraph","text":"自己的劳动力出卖给自己一样。现在讲到“必","index":225,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"0ff583433c","type":"paragraph","text":"要”劳动和“剩余”劳动，也是令人非常奇怪","index":226,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"b3692b3ee6","type":"paragraph","text":"的：仿佛在我国条件下，交给社会去扩大生产、","index":227,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"78b6ce791d","type":"paragraph","text":"发展教育和保健事业以及组织国防等等的工人劳","index":228,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"8acb5bc3e8","type":"paragraph","text":"动，对于现在掌握政权的工人阶级来说，并不是","index":229,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"283349d6f1","type":"paragraph","text":"像用来满足工人及其家庭的个人需要的劳动那样","index":230,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"d3ed0eb552","type":"paragraph","text":"必要的。[第16页]","index":231,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"2ec7758062","type":"paragraph","text":"三关于社会主义制度下的价值法则问题","index":232,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"85e8f9f05e","type":"paragraph","text":"+..。","index":233,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"7208223101","type":"paragraph","text":"....在我们的企业中，这样一些问题，如经","index":234,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"b88a2fdea9","type":"paragraph","text":"济核算和赢利问题、成本问题、价格问题等等，","index":235,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"7d218519d7","type":"paragraph","text":"就具有现实的意义。所以，我们的企业是不能不","index":236,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"fa6a06a24c","type":"paragraph","text":"而且不应该不考虑到价值法则的。","index":237,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"7bb01db250","type":"paragraph","text":"这好不好呢？这并不坏。在我国现今条件","index":238,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"c05a95868f","type":"paragraph","text":"下，（1）这的确不坏，因为这种情况教育我们的四条","index":239,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"5a06ec25f0","type":"paragraph","text":"经济工作人员来合理进行生产，并使他们遵守纪","index":240,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"7ca630f4b1","type":"paragraph","text":"律。（2）其所以不坏，是因为这种情况教我们的","index":241,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"3c2a51f73a","type":"paragraph","text":"经济工作人员计算生产量，精确地计算生产量，","index":242,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"e203b8186d","type":"paragraph","text":"并且同样精确地估量生产中的现实事物，而不去","index":243,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"ee8532bd8e","type":"paragraph","text":"修谈凭空想出来的“大概数字”。（3）其所以不","index":244,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"259c874a6f","type":"paragraph","text":"坏，是因为这种情况教我们的经济工作人员寻","index":245,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"a46bae0ccb","type":"paragraph","text":"求、发现和利用生产内部潜在的后备力量，而不","index":246,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"1a15ae3f2b","type":"paragraph","text":"去槽端它们。（4）其所以不坏，是因为这种情况","index":247,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"291f2916ed","type":"paragraph","text":"教我们的经济工作人员不是经过一些时候，才会","index":248,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"d182af01e9","type":"paragraph","text":"被改造得适合于生产力的性质。[第17页]","index":249,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"1e55fc0d34","type":"paragraph","text":"下面这个论断也是完全不正确的，就是说在","index":250,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"012596c57c","type":"paragraph","text":"我们现今的经济制度下，即在共产主义社会发展","index":251,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"fb3d3daba9","type":"paragraph","text":"的第一阶段上，价值法则仿佛调节着各个不同生","index":252,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"8ccfe073df","type":"paragraph","text":"产部门间劳动分配的“比例”值得研究","index":253,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"c506514708","type":"paragraph","text":"假如这是正确的，那就不能理解，为什么在","index":254,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"f0f91023d1","type":"paragraph","text":"我国，没有用全力去发展那比起往往赢利较少而","index":255,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"e324723849","type":"paragraph","text":"且有时简直不能赢利的重工业说来是最能赢利的","index":256,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"96a46fb76b","type":"paragraph","text":"轻工业？[第20页]","index":257,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"ed00a91973","type":"paragraph","text":"答A·V·诺特京同志","index":258,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"3084bca91d","type":"paragraph","text":"商品是这样的一种产品，它可以出售给任何","index":259,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"fe07e1d1dc","type":"paragraph","text":"买主，而且在商品出售之后，商品所有者便失去","index":260,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"3519421758","type":"paragraph","text":"对商品的所有权，而买主则变成商品的所有者，","index":261,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"5560eba0ee","type":"paragraph","text":"可以出售给他可以把商品转售、抵押或让它腐烂。生产资料人民公社","index":262,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"03ca33cf3c","type":"paragraph","text":"是否适合于这个定义呢？显然，是不适合的。第","index":263,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"0e517a39af","type":"paragraph","text":"一，生产资料，并不“出售”给任何买主，甚至","index":264,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"f60e46b875","type":"paragraph","text":"不“出售”给集体农庄，而只是由国家分配给自","index":265,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"faa8e2ff6a","type":"paragraph","text":"已的企业。第二，生产资料所有者——国家，在","index":266,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"82cff4b24c","type":"paragraph","text":"把生产资料交给某一个企业时，丝毫不失去对它","index":267,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"18eff14f9e","type":"paragraph","text":"们的所有权，相反地，是完全保持着所有权的。","index":268,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"7eb69756b9","type":"paragraph","text":"第三，企业的管理，从国家手中取得了生产资料","index":269,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"40dc3d80f2","type":"paragraph","text":"之后，不但不变成这些生产资料的所有者，相反","index":270,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"1e1e774a72","type":"paragraph","text":"地，是被确认为受苏维埃国家的委任，依照国家所","index":271,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"6075cb97b9","type":"paragraph","text":"交下的计划，来使用这些生产资料的。[第46页]","index":272,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"b9a0c24e7c","type":"paragraph","text":"价值法则对于农业原料价格的影响无论如何","index":273,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"fd6af3b743","type":"paragraph","text":"不会是有调节作用的。第一，我国农业原料的价","index":274,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"bcc5539e3f","type":"paragraph","text":"格是固定的，由计划规定的，而不是“自由”应研究","index":275,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"d50390f327","type":"paragraph","text":"的。第二，农业原料的生产规模并不是由自发的","index":276,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"31f9242c98","type":"paragraph","text":"力量，不是由什么偶然的因素来决定，而是由计","index":277,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"1b218c99b0","type":"paragraph","text":"划来决定的。第三，为生产农业原料所必需的生","index":278,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"fb8cff19c8","type":"paragraph","text":"产工具，不是集中在个别人或个别集团手中，而","index":279,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"422ce8544e","type":"paragraph","text":"是集中在国家手中。既然这样，还有什么价值法","index":280,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"},{"id":"5020bbbe9b","type":"paragraph","text":"则的调节作用呢？[第49页]","index":281,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3"}],"page":{"id":"9ceb05ca3b","publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"36228cafa3","start":135,"end":154}}}},"__N_SSG":true}